author: Trumbull Times
title: Girls soccer: Trumbull shuts out Hilltoppers
text:
By Trumbull Times on October 13, 2015 in FCIAC , High School Sports , Sports Features · 0 Comments 
The Trumbull High girls soccer team improved to 5-4-2 after coach Daniel Uhrlass’ Eagles made short work of Bridgeport Central on Tuesday, winning a 7-0 decision. 
Scoring goals were Jillian Presser, Ashley Storino, Isabelle Malakpour, Ally Coarse, Meghan Lesko, Lauren Coty and Skylar Jorge.
